tweet: Anxiety can be a big issue for all those like myself on the @Autism spectrum. I also have Generalized Anxiety Disorder, which means I worry 24/7 & find it hard to relax. However, I find keeping myself occupied & trying to keep a positive mindset can help #AutismAwarenessWeek

tweet: I was diagnosed with Aspergers Syndrome at the age of 19, and since then its had its challenges. I also have Generalized Anxiety Disorder, but I accept my positive and negative traits, and try to better myself with everyday @Autism #AutismAwarenessWeek #acceptance
